snippet.title: House Party: Murder Mystery Expansion Pack Tentacle Teaser
snippet.description:
What’s that coming out of the hot tub?! 🐙

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Did you find all of the secret codes hidden in our Steam News or Social Media posts? 

Congratulations - you've earned a secret inside sneak peek at a special exclusive teaser video for the next guest DLC, releasing this Summer 2023.

Let us know what you think's going down in the next expansion pack!

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Wishlist the House Party - Murder Mystery Expansion Pack now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1524910/House_Party__Murder_Mystery_Expansion_Pack/
